<body>
  <div class="row">

    <div class="eight columns">
      <h3>Welcome<%= if current_user.name.to_s != "" then ", " + current_user.name else "" end %>!</h3>

      <div class="profile_projects">
        <h4>Your Projects</h4>
        <% @favorite_projects.present? && @favorite_projects.each do |project| %>
          <ul>
            <li><%= link_to project.name, project_path(project) %></li>
          </ul>
        <% end %>

        <p>No favorites yet? Browse more <%= link_to "projects to change the world", projects_path %>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="profile_montage">
        <h4>Your CodeMontage</h4>

        <p>In the future, here's where your personalized CodeMontage will be! We believe everyone, not just Rocky, deserves a sweet animation that makes incredible progress look easy.</p>

        <p>In the meantime, if there are features or data or anything else you'd like in order to change the world, please <%= mail_to "hello@codemontage.com", "let us know", :subject => "Suggestion for CodeMontage" %>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
